<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>LORD DISMISS ME</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Vang ei pie'n, ei kikhen sakin,
 Kipahna, muonna ei pie'n;
 Na hehpihna nei chiet ung kau,
 Hehpih a tat guolzoin.

[V2]
 Ei hihhalh in (2)
 Gamthipa ka zin sung in.

[V3]
 2. Kipahna, zahna ka hun pieu,
 Na Chanchin Pha thu ziekin;
 Nei hukdamna zieka gah chuh,
 Ka lung u ah cheng zing hen.

[V4]
 Thudik a chun (2)
 Ginum takin um zing kau.

[V5]
 3. Lei apata sapdawk nading,
 Tiemteh na a hung um tieng
 Angel tha'n ei pawto intin,
 Sapna kipak zuiin.

[V6]
 Kum khawsawt in (2)
 Krista tawh vaihawm tang ka.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>186</hymn_number>
</song>